Created 1.4.1950 from the parishes of Bridgerule East and Bridgerule 
    West. See also Table 2, notes (h), (i) and (l).
Abolished 1.4.1950 and added to the parish of Bridgerule.

Transferred from Cornwall to Devon on 20.10.1844. Abolished 1.4.1950 
    and added to the parish of Bridgerule.

Created 1.4.1900 from the rural part of the parish of Holsworthy. 
    See also Table 2, note (l).

On 20.10.1844 the part in Devon was transfererd to Cornwall, so that thereafter North Tamerton was 
    entirely in Cornwall. 
    See also Table 2, note (f).
